---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/layout/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
    title="Contacto — edd n' dev"
    description="Cuéntanos qué necesitas construir y te diremos si conviene un sitio, un e-commerce, una automatización o software a medida."
>
    
    <!-- HEADER / HERO -->
    <div id="contact-hero" class="relative pt-32 lg:pt-48 pb-16 lg:pb-32 px-6 sm:px-12 max-w-[1800px] mx-auto min-h-[50vh] flex flex-col justify-end">
        
        <!-- Decoration: Message Bubble -->
        <div id="ledding-hero-message" class="hidden lg:block absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full z-0 opacity-60 mix-blend-screen pointer-events-none"></div>

        <div class="lg:w-3/4 relative z-10">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 opacity-70">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
                <span class="font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-gray-300">CUÉNTANOS EL CONTEXTO</span>
            </div>

            <h1 class="font-black tracking-tighter text-white leading-[0.85] text-[clamp(3.5rem,10vw,10rem)] mix-blend-screen mb-8">
                CUÉNTANOS <br>
                <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-purple-200">QUÉ NECESITAS.</span>
            </h1>

            <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-300 font-light leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
                Si necesitas una web distinta, un e-commerce propio, una automatización con IA o software a medida, escríbenos con el problema y la meta del proyecto. Te diremos si conviene construir, iterar o replantear el enfoque.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MAIN GRID -->
    <div class="border-t border-white/10 bg-[#050505] w-full">
        <div class="max-w-[1800px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 divide-y lg:divide-y-0 lg:divide-x divide-white/10 border-b border-white/10">
            
            <!-- COLUMN 1: CONTACT METHODS -->
            <div class="px-6 sm:px-12 py-24 lg:py-32 space-y-12">

                <div class="bg-[#080808] border border-white/10 p-8 sm:p-12">
                    <span class="block font-mono text-xs text-purple-400 tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Antes de escribir</span>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Qué nos ayuda a responder mejor</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-400 text-sm sm:text-base font-light leading-relaxed">
                        <li>Qué necesitas construir o mejorar.</li>
                        <li>Qué problema de negocio quieres resolver.</li>
                        <li>Si ya existe una web, tienda, sistema o proceso manual.</li>
                        <li>Tiempos, alcance y cualquier restricción importante.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Email Card -->
                <div class="group relative bg-[#080808] border border-white/10 p-8 sm:p-12 transition-colors hover:border-purple-500/50">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-6 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <span class="block font-mono text-xs text-gray-500 tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Correo Electrónico</span>
                    <a href="mailto:contacto@eddndev.com" class="block text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white group-hover:text-purple-300 transition-colors break-words">
                        contacto@eddndev.com
                    </a>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400 text-sm font-light">
                        Ideal para proyectos con contexto, alcance o requerimientos específicos. Respondemos en menos de 24 horas.
                    </p>
                </div>

                 <!-- WhatsApp Card -->
                 <div class="group relative bg-[#080808] border border-white/10 p-8 sm:p-12 transition-colors hover:border-green-500/50">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-6 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <span class="block font-mono text-xs text-gray-500 tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Chat Directo</span>
                    <a href="https://wa.me/525619433938" target="_blank" class="block text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white group-hover:text-green-300 transition-colors">
                        +52 56 1943 3938
                    </a>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400 text-sm font-light">
                        Mejor para primeras preguntas, validar encaje o coordinar una llamada breve.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Social Grid -->
                <div>
                     <span class="block font-mono text-xs text-gray-500 tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 pl-1">Redes Sociales</span>
                     <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/eddndev" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 border border-white/5 hover:bg-white/5 hover:border-white/20 transition-all text-sm text-gray-300 hover:text-white group">
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-blue-500 rounded-full group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform"></span>
                            LinkedIn
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://github.com/eddndev" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 border border-white/5 hover:bg-white/5 hover:border-white/20 transition-all text-sm text-gray-300 hover:text-white group">
                             <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-white rounded-full group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform"></span>
                            GitHub
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://instagram.com/_eddndev" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 border border-white/5 hover:bg-white/5 hover:border-white/20 transition-all text-sm text-gray-300 hover:text-white group">
                             <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-pink-500 rounded-full group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform"></span>
                            Instagram
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://github.com/achronyme" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 border border-white/5 hover:bg-white/5 hover:border-white/20 transition-all text-sm text-gray-300 hover:text-white group">
                             <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-purple-500 rounded-full group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform"></span>
                            Achronyme
                        </a>
                     </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            <!-- COLUMN 2: OFFICE / FORM PLACEHOLDER / MAP -->
            <div class="relative bg-[#020202] overflow-hidden min-h-[500px] flex flex-col justify-center">
                
                <!-- Ledding Decoration -->
                <div id="ledding-contact-container" class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-60"></div>

                <!-- Vignette / Overlay -->
                 <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#020202] via-transparent to-[#020202] pointer-events-none z-10"></div>
                 <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#020202]/50 via-transparent to-[#020202]/50 pointer-events-none z-10"></div>
                
                <div class="relative z-20 px-6 sm:px-12 py-16 lg:py-20">
                    <div class="max-w-xl border border-white/10 bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 sm:p-10">
                        <span class="block font-mono text-xs text-purple-400 tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Encaje ideal</span>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Trabajamos mejor cuando el proyecto necesita claridad técnica y criterio de producto</h2>
                        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 text-sm sm:text-base font-light leading-relaxed">
                            <li>Marcas que necesitan una presencia digital con identidad fuerte.</li>
                            <li>Negocios que quieren dejar atrás plataformas o procesos que limitan su operación.</li>
                            <li>Equipos que necesitan automatizar tareas reales, no solo añadir herramientas.</li>
                            <li>Proyectos donde rendimiento, control y experiencia visual importan al mismo tiempo.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <Footer />
</Layout>
